ying duties\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"immediate effect\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5099}, {\"ngram\": \"a full investigation\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"the airline\", \"from\": 5131, \"to\": 5142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More on this story here: The Australian National University (ANU) says it has taken \\\"immediate and comprehensive action\\\" and \\\"unreservedly apologised\\\" after an error in timesheet processing meant it underpaid 2,290 staff by about $2m.\", \"from\": 5150, \"to\": 5385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5176, \"end\": 5210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Australian National University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\"}, {\"begin\": 5180, \"end\": 5216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian National University (ANU)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5168}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"immediate and comprehensive action\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"timesheet processing\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5339}, {\"ngram\": \"2,290 staff\", \"from\": 5359, \"to\": 5370}, {\"ngram\": \"about $2m.\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, it said the university had paid $261,000 to some 220 staff for missed payments in the 2023-2024 financial year.\", \"from\": 5387, \"to\": 5514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\